highlights.text: “Mood Swings (feat. Lil Tjay)” by Pop Smoke and Lil Tjay is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 74 spots at #54.
“my future” by Billie Eilish is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #5.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 187 weeks straight.
Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “cardigan” is the highest at #7.
